text_answer.content: These passages are challenging even though the readability is below the intended grade level.  Specifically the phrasing causes the difficulty as students may not know what the phrasing is conveying.  For example "to report his proceedings" , "we deal only in the great", and "You need not be at any pains" may lead to comprehension difficulty.  As these pile up, students may lost track of the flow of the narrative.
